<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it was because of the inscription in the book - his and his wife Harriet&apos;s initials intertwined. I don&apos;t think he could bear to let it go - he<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it was because of the inscription in the book - his and his wife Harriet's initials intertwined. I don't think he could bear to let it go - he can't bear letting any part of her go.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
